00:20:35,291 --> 00:20:38,021
- Thank you so much. - We love you.

544
00:20:38,621 --> 00:20:41,051
- Bye, Kyu Ri. - Always be healthy, ma'am.

545
00:20:41,051 --> 00:20:42,121
Take care.

546
00:20:42,991 --> 00:20:43,991
We did so well.

547
00:20:44,921 --> 00:20:47,451
