00:20:48,991 --> 00:20:51,051
- Good job. - You too.

550
00:20:51,791 --> 00:20:54,821
The others should receive a penalty. They're not here.

551
00:20:54,821 --> 00:20:57,221
- Just so you know, we gave up pork belly. - Exactly.

552
00:20:57,691 --> 00:20:59,851
- My goodness. - Ma'am!

553
00:21:00,261 --> 00:21:01,951
You can't leave just yet.

