00:21:01,951 --> 00:21:04,261
- Hello, ma'am. - Hi.

555
00:21:05,191 --> 00:21:08,151
- Hello. - One Night Two Days.

556
00:21:08,151 --> 00:21:09,851
- Nice to meet you, ma'am. - This is our team.

557
00:21:09,851 --> 00:21:12,421
- Look who it is. - This is Jong Min.

558
00:21:12,421 --> 00:21:15,551
- We'll get right to the game then. - Right.

559
00:21:15,551 --> 00:21:17,761
- Let's go. - I'm worried that I won't get anything.

