00:21:17,761 --> 00:21:19,921
You can do it. Everyone else managed to do so.

561
00:21:20,521 --> 00:21:22,591
Your time starts now.

562
00:21:23,321 --> 00:21:24,651
Someone who can't sing.

563
00:21:25,121 --> 00:21:26,261
- He can't carry a tune. - A tone-deaf.

564
00:21:27,491 --> 00:21:28,521
- Nice. - That is correct.

