00:21:28,521 --> 00:21:30,451
Which network does our show air on?

566
00:21:30,451 --> 00:21:32,191
- The Korea... - Which network are we on?

567
00:21:32,191 --> 00:21:33,191
KBS1.

568
00:21:33,291 --> 00:21:34,991
- KBS1. - That is correct.

569
00:21:34,991 --> 00:21:37,221
- Next question. - Come on.

570
00:21:37,221 --> 00:21:38,391
She said "KBS1".

571
00:21:38,391 --> 00:21:39,651
- Then... - KBS2.

572
00:21:39,651 --> 00:21:40,821
- Omit the number. - KBS.

