00:22:11,591 --> 00:22:12,691
(the husband makes the coffee.)

588
00:22:12,991 --> 00:22:14,721
Sir, that's more than enough.

589
00:22:14,721 --> 00:22:15,951
We're fine with just that.

590
00:22:15,951 --> 00:22:17,891
I boiled a whole pot of water though.

591
00:22:18,591 --> 00:22:21,121
(He ends up giving everyone a cup.)

592
00:22:21,891 --> 00:22:23,951
- Here you go. - This wasn't necessary.

593
00:22:24,751 --> 00:22:26,321
Are you going to take it away? He made it for us.

594
00:22:27,191 --> 00:22:29,191
- He's right. - I'll only allow one cup.

595
00:22:29,521 --> 00:22:31,591
(Take that!)

596
00:22:32,721 --> 00:22:34,821
You all should have a cup of coffee too.

597
00:22:34,821 --> 00:22:35,821
Thank you, sir.

598
00:22:35,821 --> 00:22:37,191
(He makes sure the staff all gets one too.)

