00:25:42,191 --> 00:25:43,421
- It's a lot. - Rice with beans.

694
00:25:43,421 --> 00:25:45,651
It wasn't easy to get rice as they usually cook rice...

695
00:25:45,651 --> 00:25:46,721
- just before they eat. - Right.

696
00:25:46,721 --> 00:25:48,091
It was hard.

697
00:25:48,091 --> 00:25:50,991
That's very tempting.

698
00:25:50,991 --> 00:25:52,691
It'd go well with our food.

699
00:25:53,221 --> 00:25:54,291
All right.

