727
00:26:42,221 --> 00:26:43,951
- It must be delicious. - It's dried whole persimmon.

728
00:26:43,951 --> 00:26:45,421
It melts away in your mouth.

729
00:26:45,421 --> 00:26:47,251
- It's good. - I tried it earlier.

730
00:26:47,451 --> 00:26:48,721
And...

731
00:26:49,151 --> 00:26:50,421
Jong Min, take this.

732
00:26:50,621 --> 00:26:52,121
This is for dessert.

733
00:26:52,121 --> 00:26:53,791
All you have is desserts.

734
00:26:53,951 --> 00:26:55,621
Why is that?

