00:27:01,451 --> 00:27:02,991
- Do you have something else? - Yes.

739
00:27:02,991 --> 00:27:04,451
We have something more.

740
00:27:04,451 --> 00:27:06,191
On the way back to the base camp,

741
00:27:06,191 --> 00:27:07,921
we got some ramyeon.

742
00:27:08,151 --> 00:27:09,321
That's good.

