991
00:36:04,851 --> 00:36:07,391
Don't say that. We were so moved.

992
00:36:07,391 --> 00:36:08,591
Your poems are beautiful.

993
00:36:08,591 --> 00:36:12,121
- You're embarrassing me. - I'm serious.

994
00:36:12,891 --> 00:36:15,391
You must be learning to write.

995
00:36:15,391 --> 00:36:16,661
Are you learning to write?

996
00:36:16,661 --> 00:36:20,051
- Yes. Twice a week in the evening. - Okay.

997
00:36:20,291 --> 00:36:24,091
- On Tuesdays and Thursdays. - I see.

998
00:36:24,661 --> 00:36:26,891
