00:36:31,091 --> 00:36:32,821
Please take a look.

1001
00:36:32,821 --> 00:36:35,451
(She's their passionate teacher.)

1002
00:36:36,391 --> 00:36:39,891
(The students are even more passionate than her!)

1003
00:36:40,661 --> 00:36:41,991
(I got a perfect score!)

