1010
00:37:04,291 --> 00:37:08,991
So I decided to learn it no matter what...

1011
00:37:08,991 --> 00:37:12,891
and study as hard as I could until I'm able.

1012
00:37:12,891 --> 00:37:15,021
- You're amazing. - I'll stop only when I can't walk.

1013
00:37:15,021 --> 00:37:18,721
You wrote "Studying is needed in my life".

1014
00:37:18,851 --> 00:37:21,051
You mentioned it in your poem.

1015
00:37:21,191 --> 00:37:23,191
- Ma'am. - Yes?

1016
00:37:23,191 --> 00:37:27,161
