1031
00:38:03,091 --> 00:38:05,291
The pheasants are eating the beans...

1032
00:38:05,291 --> 00:38:07,191
and also her poems.

1033
00:38:07,191 --> 00:38:08,751
They're eating up her time too.

1034
00:38:08,751 --> 00:38:09,751
