1036
00:38:11,821 --> 00:38:15,891
That poem written by Kang Jeom Soon...

1037
00:38:15,921 --> 00:38:19,191
won the Flower Prize at the national elderly...

1038
00:38:19,191 --> 00:38:21,591
exhibition of illustrated poems.

1039
00:38:21,591 --> 00:38:23,091
